---
title: "Vico Agent — 当前执行时序"
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    actor U as 👤 用户
    participant REPL as CLI REPL
    participant AL as AgentLoop
    participant CTX as ContextManager
    participant LLM as LLM Provider
    participant TK as ToolRegistry / Tools
    participant UI as TerminalRenderer

    U->>REPL: 输入 "给电脑做体检"
    REPL->>UI: start_waiting()
    REPL->>AL: run(user_input)
    AL->>CTX: add_user_message(...)
    AL->>CTX: maybe_compress(system_prompt)

    Note over AL,LLM: ── Turn 1：同一个 Agent Loop 规划并请求工具 ──

    AL->>LLM: stream(LLMRequest, tools=tool_defs)
    LLM-->>UI: ReasoningChunk → on_thinking()
    LLM-->>UI: TextChunk → on_text("<plan>...</plan>")
    LLM-->>AL: ToolCallChunk × 6
    LLM-->>AL: DoneChunk → usage
    AL->>CTX: add_assistant_message(text, tool_calls)
    AL->>UI: on_tool_call() × 6

    alt 任一工具需要审批
        AL->>TK: 串行 execute()，逐个 request_approval()
    else 全部自动批准
        AL->>TK: asyncio.gather(execute × 6)
    end

    Note right of TK: bash/read/search/write/edit<br/>由工具风险级别决定是否审批
    TK-->>AL: ToolResult × 6
    AL->>UI: on_tool_result() × 6
    AL->>CTX: add_tool_result() × 6
    AL->>CTX: maybe_compress(system_prompt)

    Note over AL,LLM: ── Turn 2：继续观察结果并补充动作 ──

    AL->>LLM: stream(LLMRequest, tools=tool_defs)
    LLM-->>AL: ToolCallChunk × 3
    AL->>TK: dispatch_tool_calls()
    TK-->>AL: ToolResult × 3
    AL->>CTX: add_tool_result() × 3

    Note over AL,LLM: ── Turn 3：最终输出 ──

    AL->>LLM: stream(LLMRequest, tools=tool_defs)
    LLM-->>UI: TextChunk → Markdown 报告
    LLM-->>AL: DoneChunk (无工具调用)
    AL->>CTX: add_assistant_message(text, tool_calls=[])
    AL-->>REPL: 本轮完成
    REPL->>UI: flush_async() + print_context_stats()
    REPL-->>U: 显示体检报告
